A(n)
A(n+1)
\displaystyle \sum_{i=1}^n (-1)^{i+1} i^2=(-1)^{n+1}\frac 12 n(n+1)
A(n+1)
A(n+1)
\begin {align} \sum_{i=1}^{n+1} (-1)^{i+1} i^2&=(-1)^{n+1}\frac 12 n(n+1)+(-1)^{n+2}(n+1)^2 \\&=(-1)^{n+2}\left((n+1)^2-\frac 12n(n+1) \right)\\&=(-1)^{n+2}\left((n+1)(n+1-\frac 12n) \right)\\&=(-1)^{n+2}\left(\frac 12(n+1)(n+2) \right)\end {align}
